Evil Authority	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.DiscipleOfAsmodeusClassFeatures.SpecialAttack.SpellLike	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:Once per day, at the command of a disciple of Asmodeus of 6th level or higher, all evil-aligned creatures within 50 feet that have fewer Hit Dice than the disciple must succeed at a Will saving throw (DC 10 + disciple'sclass level + disciple's Cha bonus) or recognize the disciple as their superior. Affected creatures do not attack the disciple of Asmodeus and do as he commands as though affected by a mass suggestion spell. This mind-affecting ability lasts for 24 hours.	KEY:Disciple of Asmodeus ~ Evil Authority	DESC:Will DC %1.|EvilAuthorityDC			DEFINE:EvilAuthorityDC|0					BONUS:VAR|EvilAutorityDC|DefaultSpellDCCha+DiscipleOfAsmodeusLVL	BONUS:VAR|EvilAutorityDC|2|PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=FEAT,Ability Focus (Evil Authority)								ABILITY:Ability Focus|AUTOMATIC|Evil Authority								SORTKEY:Class_Disciple_Of_Asmodeus	SOURCEPAGE:BoVD	
